FINANCIAL SERVICES CLOUD ADMIN GUIDE
Work with the Sample App for Onboarding Applicants

Available in: Lightning Experience in Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions that have the Financial Services Cloud enabled

To initiate the onboarding process for applicants, launch the sample Onboarding app, create a lead record for an applicant, and then convert the lead to an opportunity.

Use the Flow Orchestration Work Guide component on the application form record page to select a product for the applicant.

Provide applicant details for Know Your Customer (KYC) verification by completing the assessment form thatâ€™s created for each applicant.

Validate identity verification and risk screening status through the Work Guide component on the applicant's party profile record page.

Validate documents in Document Checklist Items against data from the party profile and its child records.

When all applicant records are approved, set the application form record associated with them to Approved.
